  "description": "A reddish-brown squirrel is captured clinging upside down to a bare branch of a tree. The squirrel\u2019s bushy tail curves dramatically above its head, and its body is stretched downwards. Small, pale green buds are beginning to emerge on the branches, suggesting early spring. The background is a clear, bright blue sky. The branch is relatively thin and appears to be part of a larger network of branches. The squirrel is looking towards the camera with a curious expression.",
